      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@\n+---\n+title: Easier multi-key deduplication\n+type: change\n+authors: mavam\n+pr: 5570\n+---\n+\n+We now support multiple keys for deduplication, e.g., `deduplicate a, b.c, d`\n+is now equivalent to the previously unwieldy expression `deduplicate {x: a, y:\n+b.c, z: d}`."
